{"tid":325766,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[Postcrossing] 與世界各地交換明信片和郵票 （6）","createTime":"2017-07-17T12:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T12:43:58.000Z","uid":91492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e39ca48a65dc5fcb2b9da945f0014274aa0e2a9","tid":325766,"uid":91492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T12:38:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/c5/Postcrossing_Logo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fc%2Fc5%2FPostcrossing_Logo.png&h=16639157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPostcrossing 目前已有約60萬玩家，<br />\n分佈在世界各地212個國家地區內，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>參與者可以收到來自全世界的明信片。</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">寄出一張明信片的參與者可以收到至少一張來自其他國家參與者的明信片。</span></strong><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">寄出明信片的總數共50名的國家。包括：<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">美國</span>　德國　<span style=\"color: green;\">芬蘭</span>　荷蘭　<span style=\"color: violet;\">俄羅斯</span> <br />\n中華人民共和國　<span style=\"color: red;\">中華民國</span>　白俄羅斯　波蘭　<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">英國</span>　烏克蘭　日本 \t加拿大　葡萄牙　澳洲　<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">法國</span>　立陶宛　<span style=\"color: maroon;\">捷克</span>　巴西 \t<span style=\"color: red;\">義大利</span> \t西班牙 <br />\n比利時　愛沙尼亞　<span style=\"color: maroon;\">瑞士</span>　奧地利　馬來西亞　<br />\n泰國 　土耳其　香港　拉脫維亞　新加坡　<span style=\"color: teal;\">紐西蘭</span>　<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">挪威</span>　斯洛維尼亞　<span style=\"color: teal;\">羅馬尼亞</span>　匈牙利　<span style=\"color: gold;\">愛爾蘭共和國</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">瑞典</span>　<span style=\"color: navy;\">南韓</span>　菲律賓　克羅埃西亞　<span style=\"color: brown;\">印度</span>　印尼　<br />\n希臘　南非　<span style=\"color: violet;\">丹麥</span>　斯洛伐克　以色列　盧森堡　<span style=\"color: blue;\">冰島</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>註冊教學：</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/6a6W0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6a6W0.png&h=c5fb99c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>抽地址教學：</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hvv3i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fhvv3i.png&h=4220fe77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>寫卡教學：</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">點按Send a Postcard＞<br />\nRequest address</span></span></strong><br />\n就會隨機抽取到一則地址，就是明信片需要寄往的地方。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/v9Tqh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fv9Tqh.png&h=95dfd54e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/24Hvp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F24Hvp.jpg&h=e61e3ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抽取到地址後，會同時出現一組POSTCARD ID，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>必需將ID寫於明信片上</strong></span>，<br />\n收件者會用此ID登錄證實已經收到你的明信片。<br />\n當對方收到明信片後，系統會自動把你的地址隨機派給世界各地的朋友，<br />\n等待一張陌生的明信片出現在你信箱。<br />\n<br />\n官方網站：<a href=\"http://www.postcrossing.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.postcrossing.com&d=sCocSN2yEkpdpwFnpEc9JYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=0c9a82c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.postcrossing.com</a><br />\n登入成為會員，填寫基本資料，最重要是填寫正確地址。<br />\n<br />\nCredit: 暴君薯圈<br />\n感謝巴打 比我copy 佢個教學</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6b0cb4f6e7044742e56e326f32cf0f5163607e34","tid":325766,"uid":91492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T12:39:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>常見問題</strong></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">寫明信片語言？</span><br />\n答：多數用英文溝通，如遇上亞洲玩家，當時可以寫中文。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">寫地址常見問題?</span><br />\n答：中英文都可以, 國家名一定要英文(中國、台灣最好寫中文啦，派信會快D)<br />\n通常寫右邊，郵票貼右上角<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">郵票幾錢？</span><br />\n答：香港本地$1.7，國際$3.7-3.8，差唔多全世界寄野最平。<br />\n<strong>第一區 - $2.9<br />\n亞洲（日本除外）<br />\n<br />\n第二區 - $3.7<br />\n日本、大洋洲、歐洲(東歐及北歐除外)及北美洲<br />\n<br />\n第三區 - $3.8<br />\n東歐、北歐、俄羅斯、南美洲、非洲及其他目的地</strong><br />\n<ins>詳細DOWNLOAD 番HKPOST APP 查下</ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">收到明信片一定要登陸ID？</span><br />\n答：<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一定要</span></strong></span>，因為咁先會繼續將你地址派出去。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">進階交換？</span><br />\n答：於Postcrossing內可以寫個人檔案，將你想收到明信片的類別寫低，外國朋友會因你喜好已寄送明信片給你<br />\n甚至銀幣，郵票，樹葉，茶包，咖啡，零食等等等．．．．<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">交換完後可以成為筆友？</span><br />\n答：當收到明信片後你可以回覆留言比佢，可以查詢直接交朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港咩地方買到明信片?</span><br />\n答：香港郵政局、各大科學館藝術館、碼頭、書店、二手書店、文青市集，香港郵意，重慶大慶隔黎巷，錦繡唐朝"},{"pid":"5ba7843217dc3e6eaf493b759a300186ce01aecd","tid":325766,"uid":91492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T12:41:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">舊連登post </span></span></strong><br />\n1. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/236938/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/236938/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n2. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/255706/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/255706/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n3. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/278608/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/278608/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n4. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/298816/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/298816/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n5. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/308660/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/308660/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n高登都有, 有興趣可以自己google 下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: large;\">進階玩法</span><br />\n<br />\n另外仲可以係官方forum （<a href=\"https://forum.postcrossing.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.postcrossing.com&d=sCocSN2yEkpdpwFnpEc9JYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=e32c265f\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.postcrossing.com</a>）玩tag / Round Robins 去收集明信片<br />\n當然記得睇清楚人地既規則！</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a76ebae1c647b1e8723633ada8abb63740d44c09","tid":325766,"uid":91492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T12:43:58.000Z","msg":"大家去呢邊繼續<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/325762/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/325762/page/1</a>"}]}